OL,3,CMan, 85, trapped in his own home as
OL,4,Capartment lift broken for almost a
OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FAn man from Penrith has said he feels
OL,8,Flike a prisoner in his own home after
OL,9,Fthe lift in his apartment building
OL,10,Fstopped working.
OL,12,FJohn Denwood, who is 85-years-old
OL,13,Flives on the first floor of Allweights
OL,14,FHouse and hasn't been outside for
OL,15,Falmost a month because he can't tackle
OL,16,Fthe stairs.
OL,18,FDuring a routine biannual inspection
OL,19,Fof the lift in September, urgent works
OL,20,Fwere identified and it was decided the
OL,21,Flift could not continue to be used.
