OL,4,Capartment lift broken for almost a
OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FBut that has meant John, and many
OL,8,Fother residents who have health
OL,9,Fcomplications, either struggle to use
OL,10,Fthe stairs or can't use them at all.
OL,12,F"I'm feeling a bit depressed because
OL,13,Fof it," John said.
OL,15,F"I don't want to get like that, if I
OL,16,Fcan really help it, I don't, but I
OL,17,Fthink there's a limit to being stuck
OL,18,Fin here.
