OL,3,CMan, 85, trapped in his own home as
OL,4,Capartment lift broken for almost a
OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,F"I'm going to get worse until I can
OL,8,Fget out and have a good chinwag, which
OL,9,FI'm missing it because I'm not seeing
OL,10,Fanybody to talk to.
OL,12,F"I need some fresh air. The only fresh
OL,13,Fair I get is from the window."
OL,15,FJohn's daughter, Alison, comes to
OL,16,Fvisit when she can, but she can't help
OL,17,Fbut worry about how being cooped up
OL,18,Finside is wearing on her dad.
