OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FShe said: "I'll continue to do it, but
OL,8,Fit would be nice for him to get out
OL,9,Fand get a bit of his own freedom back
OL,10,Fagain and he can do what he wants and
OL,11,Fgo and see who he wants when he wants.
OL,13,F"It's not nice because it upsets me. I
OL,14,Fwant him out and about but when he's
OL,15,Fjust sat and that's all he's doing -
OL,16,Fit's upsetting. It's it's not nice at
OL,17,Fall."
