OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FResidents have been told their service
OL,8,Fcharge will have to increase in order
OL,9,Fto front the repair bill, which is
OL,10,Festimated to cost #8200.
OL,12,F"They pay a service charge every week
OL,13,Fas it is which is supposed to cover
OL,14,Fthings like this but now they have
OL,15,Fbeen told they have to pay more,"
OL,16,FAlison said.
OL,18,F"Why do they have to pay extra?"
