OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Riverside Group,
OL,8,Fwhich manages the building, said:
OL,9,F""We're very sorry for any
OL,10,Finconvenience caused by the lift being
OL,11,Fout of service at Allweights House,
OL,12,Fand want to reassure residents that
OL,13,Fwe're doing everything we can to put
OL,14,Fthings right.
OL,16,F"We've kept in touch with residents
OL,17,Fthroughout and have visited Mr Denwood
OL,18,Fto discuss any support he may need.
