OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,F"We're committed to resolving this
OL,8,Fquickly and safely and will continue
OL,9,Fto keep residents updated."
OL,11,FDue to the nature and costs of the
OL,12,Fworks, a Section 20 consultation was
OL,13,Finitially required, which would have
OL,14,Fdelayed repairs until November.
